ty and CEO-designate of Mobility Global, will also join the Board alongside a group of highly-qualified directors w" /><meta name="twitter:image" content="https://mma.prnewswire.com/media/2842604/SP_Global_Logo.jpg" /><!--[if lte IE 8]>
